mile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296ca5b945744390f99fc11b14206ab9491a31eb","tid":2242033,"uid":332877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T19:00:38.000Z","msg":"中晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63944fd88fe98d06d45f0b958af64062029b7d1","tid":2242033,"uid":336804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T19:01:02.000Z","msg":"以為係自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留名圍爐"},{"pid":"1a7bded92e4e01ce4054446835abef3262522edb","tid":2242033,"uid":64476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T19:38:12.000Z","msg":"我係2<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba0a952e2dfe7175aafeea9501cc291f379887e","tid":2242033,"uid":19946,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T19:54:57.000Z","msg":"1 2都中<br />\n<br />\n可能之前識嘅人都太得人驚，會追你追到日日msg騷擾，唔敢再主動識人。<br />\n<br />\n有時淨係想做個朋友無做咩特別行為，但對方都好似會有意思咁，之後要不斷咁同人斷絕關係，好攰同時覺得可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪有啲咩感情潔癖，好怕一段關係嘅結束，所以好難先會鍾意一個人/選擇同人開始。"},{"pid":"6034df3ac929646a04bfc8611cacbc6469fb4ac1","tid":2242033,"uid":109435,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T20:13:21.000Z","msg":"第一點好準<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾對方第二次問出去date，我直情唔敢㩒入去覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怕自己唔夠好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3feb7ed34740fe46a835767092da798cd8e56ba4","tid":2242033,"uid":175345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T00:07:28.000Z","msg":"原來大家都或多或少會中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我以前無呢啲問題，或者根本唔發現自己有呢啲問題。直至我同前男友五年前分手之後(拍咗年半，係我提出分手)，再遇到嘅人同事，先發現自己有呢堆問題。<br />\n<br />\n有無人成功解決到呢啲問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2396692918df683